  "text": "The confining medium was water in the present case (confining liquids are reported in many articles 14,25-28 ), while confining solid, glass/quartz, are reported by Qiong Nian et al. [CITATION_1] . Regardless of the type of confinement, the CPLA that permits the diamond phase formation can be described as a three-step process:",
